snippet.title: Final Fantasy Legend 3 (GB) Final Battle
snippet.description:
Final Battle for Final Fantasy Legend 3 on Gameboy.

Xagor has around 50,000 HP so this battle will last a while.

I went with the same team as I did in the previous Legend games, 2 Humans and 2 Mutants. In this game I spent alot of time and got them up to level 53-55 and they have some of the best armor and spells.

Also if you notice any skips in the music or video, thats just my attempt at re-syncing the audio, the same applies to the ending videos.
